platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Save and scan recipes to try

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: This exceptional recipe manager makes every part of cooking easier. Organize recipes, create a meal calendar, and create grocery lists—then view instructions using the gorgeous cook mode. Adding new recipes is even easier: Import from URLs, scan from paper, view friends’ shared libraries, or subscribe to your favorite cooking blogs.
This exceptional recipe manager makes every part of cooking easier, from creating meal calendars and grocery lists to importing recipes from your favourite cooking blogs.

Ce fabuleux gestionnaire de recettes facilite toutes les étapes de la cuisine, qu’il s’agisse de générer le menu de la semaine, de dresser des listes de courses ou d’importer des recettes de vos blogs de cuisine préférés.
创建膳食日历，列举购物清单，管理美味食谱，这款 App 让烹饪的每一个环节都变得无可挑剔。
無論是建立膳食日曆和雜貨清單，抑或要從心水烹飪 blog 輸入食譜，這款食譜管理工具可令每個烹飪步驟變得更輕鬆簡單。
